---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Icon from "../components/ui/icons.astro";

const lastUpdated = "March 11, 2026";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions — chrod"
  description="Terms and Conditions for chrod developer portfolio."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-32 text-slate-300">
    <a
      href="/"
      class="mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500 transition-colors hover:text-red-400"
    >
      <Icon name="back" />
      Back to home
    </a>

    <h1 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="mb-12 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-10 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          1. Acceptance of Terms
        </h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using this website (<strong class="text-slate-200"
            >chrod</strong
          >), operated by Carlos Hernández, you agree to be bound by these Terms
          and Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms,
          please do not use this website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          2. Nature of This Website
        </h2>
        <p>
          This is a personal portfolio website intended to showcase my work,
          skills, and professional experience. It is not an e-commerce platform
          and does not facilitate direct purchases or automated service
          contracts. Any engagement for professional services requires a
          separate written agreement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          3. Intellectual Property
        </h2>
        <p>
          All content on this website — including but not limited to text,
          design, code, graphics, and the logo — is the property of Carlos
          Hernández and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any content from this
          website without explicit written permission, except for the purpose of
          sharing a link to this website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          4. Project Showcases
        </h2>
        <p>
          Projects displayed on this portfolio may include work done for clients
          or employers. All sensitive or confidential information has been
          omitted or anonymized. Client names, logos, or references are used
          only with permission or in accordance with public information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          5. External Links
        </h2>
        <p>
          This website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., GitHub
          repositories, live demos, LinkedIn). I am not responsible for the
          content or privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to
          review their policies independently.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          6. Disclaimer of Warranties
        </h2>
        <p>
          This website is provided "as is" without any warranties, express or
          implied. I do not guarantee that the website will be available at all
          times, error-free, or free from viruses or other harmful components.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          7. Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, I shall not be liable for any
          indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use
          of this website or from any information contained herein.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          8. Freelance Services
        </h2>
        <p>
          Inquiries submitted through the contact form or via WhatsApp do not
          constitute a binding contract or agreement. All freelance or
          consulting engagements are formalized through a separate proposal and
          signed agreement between both parties. Pricing, timelines, and
          deliverables will be established on a per-project basis.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          9. Changes to These Terms
        </h2>
        <p>
          I reserve the right to update these Terms and Conditions at any time.
          Changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date. Continued
          use of the website after changes are posted constitutes your
          acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">
          10. Governing Law
        </h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of Colombia. Any
          disputes arising from the use of this website shall be subject to the
          exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts in Colombia.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">11. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact:</p>
        <p class="mt-3 font-medium text-slate-200">
          Carlos Hernández — <a
            href="mailto:chrod.dev@gmail.com"
            class="text-red-400 hover:underline">chrod.dev@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
